kingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business finance and investment, Analyze economic growth charts for informed business finance decisions and financial decision-making. Stock Market report, Strategy, Data Collection, Forecasting\" data-id=\"2021524839\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"910px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Shutthiphong Chandaeng</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In 2024, the pace and magnitude of change became more extraordinary. The interplay of climate transition, geopolitical dynamics, and technological advancement continues to reshape the investment landscape at an unprecedented rate. Successfully navigating these transformative forces requires both adaptability and disciplined risk</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2021524839/image_2021524839.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747477-2024-macro-commentary-next-economy-forces-reshaping-markets", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 19:10:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747492", "title": "Birkenstock: There's Still Room To Rise As ASP Expansion And China Growth Power Earnings", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2013879409/image_2013879409.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Birkenstock logo on a Bonn reseller Store taken on their local boutique. Birkenstock is a shoe manufacturer famous for its sandals.\" data-id=\"2013879409\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2013879409/image_2013879409.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2013879409/image_2013879409.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2013879409/image_2013879409.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2013879409/image_2013879409.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2013879409/image_2013879409.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2013879409/image_2013879409.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2013879409/image_2013879409.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2013879409/image_2013879409.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">BalkansCat</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>With 2025 starting on a slightly down note, we note that many investors are probably sounding off cautious alarms on last year's big, momentum-driven winners. Against this backdrop, I continue to favor \"growth at a reasonable price\" stocks for my portfolio, especially those that have exhibited choppier</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2013879409/image_2013879409.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747492-birkenstock-asp-expansion-and-china-growth-power-earnings", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 19:05:08", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747405", "title": "How AI Will Redefine Broadcom In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326339/image_1196326339.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Broadcom\" data-id=\"1196326339\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326339/image_1196326339.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326339/image_1196326339.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326339/image_1196326339.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326339/image_1196326339.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326339/image_1196326339.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326339/image_1196326339.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326339/image_1196326339.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326339/image_1196326339.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">G0d4ather</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>Since the <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4722885-why-broadcom-is-ais-big-winner\">first coverage</a> on Broadcom (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AVGO\" title=\"Broadcom Inc.\">AVGO</a></span>), \"Broadcom Is AI's Big Winner,\" the stock (+33%) has massively outperformed the market S&amp;P 500 (+3%) in terms of price return. The first coverage was focused on high AI and boosted infrastructure software revenue. In</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1196326339/image_1196326339.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747405-how-ai-will-redefine-broadcom-in-2025", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 19:00:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747489", "title": "NVDX: Key Nvidia Volatility Catalysts To Begin 2025, Wait For A Pullback", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412721464/image_1412721464.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Nvidia Corporation building in Taipei, Taiwan.\" data-id=\"1412721464\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412721464/image_1412721464.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412721464/image_1412721464.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412721464/image_1412721464.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412721464